OL,3,CTeenager recalls moments before school
OL,4,Cbus burst into flames
OL,6,FA pupil on board a bus that caught
OL,7,Ffire en route to school says they were
OL,8,Fmoments away from disaster.
OL,10,FTyler Heaviside was on the bus heading
OL,11,Fto Teesdale School when the 15-year-
OL,12,Fold and his fellow pupils had to
OL,13,Fevacuate the vehicle which burst into
OL,14,Fflames seconds later on Tuesday 18
OL,15,FJune.
OL,17,FHogdsons Coach Operators Ltd said the
OL,18,Fcause of the fire has not been
OL,19,Fdetermined and regular inspections are
OL,20,Fcarried out on their vehicles.
