OL,3,CTeenager recalls moments before school
OL,4,Cbus burst into flames
OL,6,FNo one was injured in the incident,
OL,7,Fnear Barnard Castle, but Tyler
OL,8,Fbelieves the outcome could have been a
OL,9,Flot worse.
OL,11,FRecalling the morning of the fire, he
OL,12,Ftold ITV Tyne Tees it did not feel
OL,13,Fright.
OL,15,F"We went upstairs, me and my friend,
OL,16,Fand we all sat in the back of the bus
OL,17,Fupstairs, and when we got on, the
OL,18,Fseats were very hot," he said.
