OL,3,CTeenager recalls moments before school
OL,4,Cbus burst into flames
OL,6,F"If you would touch them, it would
OL,7,Flike burn your hand. We went round the
OL,8,Fcorner and then this smoke started to
OL,9,Fcome through the back of the seats
OL,10,Fwhere we were sitting.
OL,12,F"When we were actually going
OL,13,Fdownstairs from upstairs, there was an
OL,14,Fengine fluid l coming through the back
OL,15,Fof the bus, like leaking onto the
OL,16,Fyoung ones at the back.
