OL,3,CTeenager recalls moments before school
OL,4,Cbus burst into flames
OL,6,F"As soon as we got off the bus, it
OL,7,Fkind of like lit up and went straight
OL,8,Fup. It was mental because, just
OL,9,Fthinking that if we didn't stop the
OL,10,Fbus, then we probably could have died."
OL,12,FTyler was sending his dad Keith
OL,13,FHeaviside videos from the scene.
OL,15,FAnd while grateful he was safe, Mr
OL,16,FHeaviside said he and other parents
OL,17,Fare concerned and question if the bus
OL,18,Fshould have been on the road in the
OL,19,Ffirst place.
