OL,3,CTeenager recalls moments before school
OL,4,Cbus burst into flames
OL,6,F"I can't do anything about what
OL,7,Fhappened but I wouldn't like to see
OL,8,Fthis happen in the future because we
OL,9,Fmay be having a completely different
OL,10,Fconversation."
OL,12,FHodgson Coaches are contracted by
OL,13,FDurham County Council to carry out
OL,14,Fthis school run.
OL,16,FThey said: "At Hodgsons, planned
OL,17,Fmaintenance inspections are carried
OL,18,Fout on our vehicles at least every 42
OL,19,Fdays. Vehicles are also checked daily
OL,20,Fby the drivers.
