OL,3,CTeenager recalls moments before school
OL,4,Cbus burst into flames
OL,6,F"While we await the outcome of the
OL,7,Fongoing investigation to establish the
OL,8,Fcause of the fire, we wish to reassure
OL,9,Fparents and passengers that safety is
OL,10,Four number one priority.
OL,12,F"Following the incident, we have
OL,13,Farranged for additional engineers to
OL,14,Fbe available to assist depot drivers."
OL,16,FMr Heaviside has also written to the
OL,17,Fcouncil to express his concerns.
