OL,3,CTeenager recalls moments before school
OL,4,Cbus burst into flames
OL,6,FIn a statement, the council said: "We
OL,7,Fare pleased that no-one was injured
OL,8,Fduring this incident and would like to
OL,9,Fthank and praise the young people who
OL,10,Fhelped to ensure the bus was evacuated
OL,11,Fquickly.
OL,13,F"We have been in close contact with
OL,14,Fthe coach operator since the incident
OL,15,Foccurred and are awaiting the outcome
OL,16,Fof ongoing investigations."
